			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">couple ways, easiest imo is get someone with a friend with /pet hold   and then goto an arena like freeport  and beat on the pet all day u will get offense/piercing skills...     works also for defense if u have em send his pet on you.
<br />

<br />

<br />
another way but alot slower imo   is goto Paineel and theres a vendor near the Hole attack him ( he will HT once for like 400 )  and then u can melee him, u will get offense/defense skillups ( suggest getting temperance and a regen beforehand) 
<br />

<br />

<br />
and the other way is to get in a group land dots on a mob and then melee the mob while your tank is beating the crap out of it<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=1014810" target="_blank" class="postlink"><img src="http://www3.telus.net/cbriere1/rootedx.gif" border="0" /></a></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
