My dodge is maxed at 75 and my defense is at 113.  I am very very good at getting hit by things, repeatedly, and often. <img src="images/smiles/icon_smile.gif" alt="Smile" border="0" />  But when it comes time to hit back I miss about 90% of the time.  I would like to be able to do a little bit of melee damage, even if it's not much.  It could in rare cases make a little difference.  Of course as soon as I can afford a nice non-melee primary I'll pick it up.  There doesn't seem to be a great deal of mid-level gear in the game that's either affordable or attainable while in the mid-level range.<br />_________________<br />My spell book is sorted by the aesthetic appeal of the spell's effect.  Just kidding.
